    • findEligibleApplicants

      public List<Applicant> findEligibleApplicants(FlatType flatType)
      Finds applicants eligible for specific flat types based on age and marital status. - Singles, 35 years old and above, can ONLY apply for 2-Room. - Married, 21 years old and above, can apply for any flat types (2-Room or 3-Room).
      Parameters:
      flatType - The flat type to check eligibility for.
      Returns:
      List of eligible applicants.

    • hasActiveApplication

      public boolean hasActiveApplication(String applicantNric)
      Checks if an applicant has already submitted an application that is not in a final rejected/withdrawn state. Requires access to Application data - better in a Service layer.
      Parameters:
      applicantNric - The NRIC of the applicant.
      Returns:
      true if the applicant has an active/pending application, false otherwise.
